The template files for debian used here requires the developer to create extra files in the debian-src directory.

@TARNAME@.defoma-hints
This needs to be edited by hand. The best way to start this is to run something like:
    defoma-hints truetype *.ttf > debian-src/@TARNAME@.defoma-hints
(obviously replacing @TARNAME@)

copyright
An example copyright file is included as copyright.ex

README.Debian
An example is included as README.Debian.ex
